NINTENDO GAME & WATCH · node GW · GW · NINTENDO GAME & WATCH · exereunesis · handheld teardown · 1980 · UD0 / exereunesis

universe of origin : the teardown — a made machine, opened and explored
seal               : Before the Game Boy there was Game & Watch: Gunpei Yokoi's line of single-game LCD handhelds, each a calculator-grade 4-bit chip driving a fixed, pre-printed segment screen. They funded Nintendo's rise, debuted the cross-shaped D-pad, and their dual-screen models prefigured the DS.
